        NONE      - none.
        FLOYD     - Use Floyd-Steinberg dithering.
        BURKES    - Use Burkes dithering.
        STUCKI    - Use Stucki dithering.
        SIERRA    - Use Sierra dithering.
        JARVIS    - Use Jarvis dithering.
        STEVENSON - Use Stevenson-Arce dithering.

Result:
        None.

